{"tid":428701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［蝻亞建國］南亞裔向林鄭投訴公立醫院無人識「南亞裔」話","createTime":"2017-10-08T09:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T18:02:59.000Z","uid":41351,"like":3,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"27663ad2728941dc9491af1b2f293ce032898d7a","tid":428701,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:33:25.000Z","msg":"少數族裔團體「Voices of Diversity」到政府總部外遞交請願信，希望行政長官林鄭月娥正視少數族裔面對的問題，特別是醫療和教育問題。<br />\n<br />\n團體成員Jeff Andrews表示有本地幼稚園拒絕接收非本地學生，令他們缺乏學習中文的機會，導致難以融入社會。成員簡浩明指本港公營醫院缺乏翻譯員，少數族裔的香港人因為無法溝通，而未能享有公營醫療服務。<br />\n<br />\n少數族裔大學生黛雅表示對林鄭月娥有信心，希望林鄭月娥能夠在政策上顯示出對少數族裔的關注。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E6%97%8F%E8%A3%94%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E8%AB%8B%E9%A1%98%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%96%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E6%97%8F%E8%A3%94%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-082927270.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2597%258F%25E8%25A3%2594%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%25AB%258B%25E9%25A1%2598%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2597%258F%25E8%25A3%2594%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2595%258F%25E9%25A1%258C-082927270.html&d=sK2KRvT%2B3CmQkTl83yauWARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7dc8f85d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E6%97%8F%E8%A3%94%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E8%AB%8B%E9%A1%98%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%96%E5%B0%91%E6%95%B8%E6%97%8F%E8%A3%94%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-082927270.html</a><br />\n蝻開始想建立自己社區及政治版圖了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41790dde78961191b59e24a36c114f13a243f3ee","tid":428701,"uid":41508,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T09:35:57.000Z","msg